column16: Jarrod Dyson flies out to right fielder Kole Calhoun.
Mike Moustakas pops out to third baseman David Freese.
Omar Infante grounds out sharply, third baseman David Freese to first baseman Albert Pujols.
Salvador Perez flies out to center fielder Mike Trout.
Billy Butler grounds out, first baseman Albert Pujols to pitcher David Carpenter.   Lorenzo Cain to 3rd.
Eric Hosmer grounds out to first baseman Albert Pujols.   Lorenzo Cain to 2nd.
Lorenzo Cain singles on a line drive to right fielder Kole Calhoun.
Jarrod Dyson grounds out, pitcher David Carpenter to second baseman Howie Kendrick to first baseman Albert Pujols.
Alcides Escobar grounds out, shortstop Erick Aybar to first baseman Albert Pujols.
Mike Moustakas pops out to third baseman David Freese.
